resultset.statement: select ms.solarSystemId as id, ms.solarSystemName as name, ms.regionid, mr.regionname, ms.constellationid, mc.constellationname, ms.security from mapSolarSystems ms, mapRegions mr, mapConstellations mc where ms.regionid = mr.regionid and ms.constellationid = mc.constellationid and ms.security < 0 and mr.regionname not like '%-%' order by ms.solarsystemid asc
